| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4347 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b3d6fba7-3a52-51f1-8ef3-9836b860b55e"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
